     H            Y.
     F** UTLR40 ****************************************************
     F*  PROGRAM: UTILITY- GET TOYOTA BIN#                         *
     F*  WRITTEN: JW (SRA)  2020.07.10                             *
     F*------------------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'UTLR40'
     F*                    PARM           $SDATE  8
     F*                    PARM           $STIME  6
     F*                    PARM           $BIN    2
     F*                    PARM           $RTN    1
     F* ----------------------------
     F*   IN  $$SDATE 8A :  SHIP DATE
     F*       $$STIME 6A :  SHIP TIME
     F*       $$BIN   2A :  BIN#
     F*   OUT $RTN    1A :  "*" ERROR
     F******************************************************
     FAB#PP80 IF  E           K        DISK         KINFDS INF1
     E                    FM         30  4 0
     E                    TO         30  4 0
     IINF1        DS
     I                                     *STATUS  @STTS
     I                                       83  92 #FILE
     I                                       93 102 #LIB
     I                                    B 156 1590#RCNT
     I                                        1 256 ARA
     I            DS
